
____________________________________instructions__________________
- download repo
- cd to the repo
- install packages using npm : npm i
- run application using hotnode w/portnumber : hotnode app.js 9000
- navigate to the application : http://localhost:9000/

____________________________________architecture__________________
[node-express-server]
 app.js [head of the beast]
 package.json [project information and dependency list]
  - public
    -- css
      --- style.css
    -- img
      --- g.jpg
      --- w.jpg
    -- js
      --- routes.js [application page routing]
  - views
    -- pages 
      --- index.ejs
      --- page2.ejs
    -- partials [static piece of html]
      --- body.ejs
      --- head.ejs
      --- nav.ejs
